      "title": "Fuel Crisis: Limited buses in service",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Lanka Private Bus Owners Association says that a limited number of buses will be operated on Monday (1) due to the fuel shortage.",
        "The Chairman of the Lanka Private Bus Owners Association Gemunu Wijeratne said that due to insufficient fuel received in the last few days, all the buses are not able to operate."
      ],
